sentences: Dariush was born in Tehran to parents from Mianeh on February 4, 1951.
(Persian: به من نگو دوست دارم be man nagu duset dāram)He left Iran in 1978 and became a part of the diasporic music scene in Los Angeles.
He spent his early years in Mianeh, Karaj and Kurdistan province (Ostan-e Kordestan).
